just_use analyze_trick_coverage.py

# label: TOOL
# role: redundancy probe — find tricks whose firings are always shadowed

Plays N games; at every decision point records the set of
tricks that pass invariant. Trick A is a redundancy candidate
if every state where A fires has some B≠A also firing —
B could substitute for A.

Diagnostic for the older `strategy.py` trick-engine; not
load-bearing for `bfs_solver`.
